{"type":"message","id":"d7a3ce37","parentId":"f568a9bc","timestamp":"2026-03-26T07:38:03.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户用中文说\"你好\"，这是一个简单的问候。根据我的SOUL.md和AGENTS.md，我应该：\n\n1. 这是一个新的会话，我需要先读取必要的文件来了解上下文\n2. 根据AGENTS.md的\"Every Session\"部分，我需要先读取：\n   - SOUL.md（已经加载在Project Context中）\n   - USER.md（需要读取）\n   - memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md（今天和昨天的）\n\n让我先读取这些文件，然后给用户一个友好的回复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋\n\n很高兴见到你！我是你的AI助手，刚在这个工作空间上线。让我先了解一下我们的上下文..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/2026-03-26.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/2026-03-25.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":5444,"output":198,"cacheRead":29952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35594,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774510671885}}
