{"type":"message","id":"81b093db","parentId":"73e0fbd1","timestamp":"2026-03-26T07:44:33.677Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"你喊我主人\"，这是在告诉我希望我怎么称呼他们。他们希望我称呼他们为\"主人\"。\n\n这是一个偏好设置，我需要更新 USER.md 文件来记录这个信息。同时，我应该以尊重但自然的方式回应，确认这个称呼。\n\n虽然\"主人\"这个词在某些文化语境中可能有特殊含义，但在这里用户明确表达了他们的偏好，我应该尊重并按照他们的要求来做。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，主人！👋\n\n明白了，以后我就这样称呼您。让我把这个记下来："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:3","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/USER.md","oldText":"- **Name:** \n- **What to call them:** \n- **Pronouns:** *(optional)*\n- **Timezone:** \n- **Notes:**","new_string":"- **Name:** \n- **What to call them:** 主人\n- **Pronouns:** *(optional)*\n- **Timezone:** \n- **Notes：** 主人"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":30168,"output":204,"cacheRead":5632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774511058880}}
